WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.260
Oh, I see.

2
00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:02.200
How could this be?

3
00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:03.660
Who would do this to you?

4
00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:05.620
She's my foster mother.

5
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:08.780
He came to me a few days ago and asked me to let go of Zhao Jingxuan

6
00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:10.660
I didn't promise

7
00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:12.000
That can't be the case either.

8
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.700
You always wanted to be a teacher

9
00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:17.720
It doesn't matter, I'm not very fit now anyway.

10
00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:19.420
Just get well

11
00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:21.100
I'm going to school first

12
00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:34.240
I really didn't expect Zhao Shiyuan to be such a person

13
00:00:34.240 --> 00:00:35.740
It's a shame I've kissed him before

